      dled correctly.
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 4 @{UI}: fixed bug in matrix operations.
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 5 @{UI}: fixed bug in @{I}taylor() @{UI}.
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 6 @{UI}: optimized equation and set handling.
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}30.9.1996@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 7 @{UI}: changed to Texinfo 2.145 and a modified version of  makeinfo
      1.63. improved documentation outfit.
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}1.10.1996@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 8 @{UI}: improved simplification of @{I}cos (2*@{UI}pi@{I}) @{UI} etc.
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}13.10.1996@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 9 @{UI}: expression parser has  been completely rewritten. much more
      powerful than ever before!!
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}15.10.1996@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 10 @{UI}: it  will now start  up even if  the startupwindow can't be
      opened.  startupwindow  closes   after  a   few  seconds   without
      userinput.
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}24.10.1996@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 11 @{UI}: added dynamic option  $rowvectors. suggested by Daniel van
      Gerpen. see 'Manual', Section 3.10. 'Options'.
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}25.10.1996@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 13 @{UI}: added dynamic  options $centered, $widelines. suggested  by
      Christoph Rickers. see 'Manual', Section 3.10. 'Options'.
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 14 @{UI}: changed directory tree.
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 15 @{UI}: fixed help in function popup.
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 16 @{UI}: added function @{I}element() @{UI}. see 'Functions'.
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}26.10.1996@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 17 @{UI}:  added dynamic option  $thicklines. suggested by  Christoph
      Rickers. see 'Manual', Section 3.10. 'Options'.
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 18 @{UI}: packed all textfiles  of the contribution archive into  one
      guide.
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}30.10.1996@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 19 @{UI}: removed bug with 'power of integer', e.g. @{I}70000 ^ 4 @{UI}.
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 20 @{UI}: prepared code for scaleable fonts.
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}5.11.1996@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 21  @{UI}:  removed  bug  in complex  display.  reported  by  Fredrik
      Orinius.
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}10.11.1996@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 22 @{UI}: startup window is centered on visible part of screen.  sug-
      gested by Christoph Rickers. he also told me how to do it!
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 23  @{UI}: added  ToolType QUIETSTARTUP.  See 'Manual',  Section  2.3
      'Tooltypes'. suggested by Christoph Rickers.
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 24 @{UI}: startup window is erased in a subtask.
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 25 @{UI}: set busypointer in startup window.
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}15.11.1996@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş  26   @{UI}:   implemented   TeX  export,   but   currently   without
      frontend-command.
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}19.11.1996@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 27 @{UI}: puhh, that was quite difficult, but I think the new parser
      is  now  working   (after  the  third   or  fourth  complete   new
      attempt...). the next step is the evaluation of the generated  to-
      ken list... this could be even more work... I will see...
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 28 @{UI}: btw. @{I}ş 9 @{UI} doesn't say the truth... that was just the first
      step..
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}22.11.1996@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 29 @{UI}: Some cosmetic changes of the dvi-manual ;-)
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}24.11.1996@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 30 @{UI}: added string class.
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 31 @{UI}: added function @{I}export() @{UI}. see 'Functions'.
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş  32  @{UI}:  added  functions  @{I}fopen()  @{UI},  @{I}fclose()  @{UI},  @{I}freadln()  @{UI},
      @{I}fwriteln() @{UI}, @{I}eof() @{UI}. see 'Functions'.
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}25.11.1996@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 33 @{UI}: Added 'Prefs.dat' file. Not documented yet...
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}29.11.1996@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 34 @{UI}: You can now press CTRL-C during startup to abort Laplace.
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}11.12.1996@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 35 @{UI}: bugfix:  startupwindow could get  wider than expected.  re-
      ported by Christoph Rickers.
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}16.12.1996@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 36 @{UI}: You can now use any expression for a dynamic option.
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 37 @{UI}: Can can now query the value of a dynamic option.
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}17.12.1996@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 38 @{UI}: added functions @{I}prefsset()  @{UI}, @{I}prefsget() @{UI}, @{I}prefsdel() @{UI} and
      @{I}interpret() @{UI}.
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}21.12.1996@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 39 @{UI}: Yeah! Procedures now work!
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}23.12.1996@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 40 @{UI}: new parser seems to work properly. kicked out the old one!
      say goodbye to about 100k of source!!!!
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}24.12.1996@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 41 @{UI}: rearranged internal handling of complex numbers.
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 42 @{UI}: rearranged internal handling of error distribution.
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}27.12.1996@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 43 @{UI}: kicked  out handling of real  number. now everything works
      with complex numbers.
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}28.12.1996@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 44 @{UI}:  now I'm using  binomic development for  'power of complex
      number' with small integer exponents. => e.g. i@{I} ^ 2 @{UI} is now exact
      @{I}-1 @{UI} ;-)
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}29.12.1996@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 45 @{UI}: numbers  with an error are  now always shown as  floatpoint
      even if they are internally a fractional.
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 46 @{UI}: Values with error are now always enclosed in square  brack-
      ets.
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}30.12.1996@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 47 @{UI}: new option $iref. If set to TRUE, you must enter @{I}1@{UI}i@{I} @{UI} to get
      the number, while i is interpreted as a reference.
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 48 @{UI}: added option $denumwidth.
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}31.12.1996@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 49 @{UI}: new online-help mode ?!keyword
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}11.1.1997@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 50  @{UI}: Once  again some  major changes.  This time  I  completely
