 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}12.1.1997@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 51 @{UI}: added block marking facility.
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}15.1.1997@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 52 @{UI}: added subexpression feature  in reference names. See docu-
      mentation for details (not written yet ;-)
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}16.1.1997@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 53 @{UI}: optimized matrix and vector operations.
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 54 @{UI}: added boolean operation for vectors and matrices.
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}18.1.1997@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 55 @{UI}: a large  set now splits into  several lines, if it doesn't
