 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}25.1.1997@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 56 @{UI}: concat strings by adding them.
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}11.2.1997@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 57 @{UI}: bugfix: @{I}a ^ y*a ^ x  @{UI} with @{I}x+y=1 @{UI} resulted to @{I}1 @{UI}. Reported
