@{FG SHINE}@{BG SHADOW}@{B}- Anleitung zu Laplace --------------------------------------- Release V0.10 -@{FG TEXT}@{BG BACKGROUND}@{UB}

@REM KEY 0 0 "HistoryLog" "Release V0.10"
@{B}Release V0.10@{UB} (beta-release) released 29.1.1998

 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}14.1.1998@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 1 @{UI}: Changed @{I}array() @{UI} to @{I}newarray() @{UI}. I need @{B}array@{UB} for something
      else.
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 2 @{UI}: New function @{I}genarray() @{UI}.
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 3 @{UI}: Invented new type system. Changes syntax of procedure decla-
      ration, e.g. @{I}number p(vector x) { x * x; } @{UI}.
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}15.1.1998@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 4 @{UI}: There was an endless loop, when simplifying @{I}1/sqrt(x) @{UI}.
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 5 @{UI}: Startup window now uses AHI for sound replay.
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 6 @{UI}: A plotter is coming... I can see him at the horizon!
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}16.1.1998@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 7 @{UI}: After a  long, long night (I could  say 'good morning' to  a
      flatmate...), a basic function plotter is working.
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}22.1.1998@{UB}
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 8  @{UI}: Startupwindow:  AHI kicked  out again,  now uses  datatypes
      (which might use AHI, if installed...)
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 9 @{UI}:  Animated plots!!! Wasn't  very difficult,  a first version
      worked after 20mins o' codin'...
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}23.1.1998@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 10 @{UI}: You may even show multiple plot anims... >KILL YOUR PROCES-
      SOR!!!!<
 @{B}∑@{UB} @{B}28.1.1998@{UB}:
    @{B}∑@{UB} @{I}ş 11 @{UI}: Well, the plotter seems to work so far, time for a new re-
      lease...


@{FG SHINE}@{BG SHADOW}@{B}----------------------------------------------------------------- © bei P!\K -@{FG TEXT}@{BG BACKGROUND}@{UB}
